={
  "query": "
  query SYNC_CHAT_MESSAGES(
    $isLive: Boolean = false
    $protocol: String!
    $limit: Int = 50
    $before: Date
    $after: Date
  ) {
    getChatMessages(
      isLive: $isLive
      limit: $limit
      before: $before
      after: $after
      protocol: $protocol
    ) {
      docs {
        id
        ref
        type
        direction
        payload
        reply {
          id
          ref
          type
          payload
          direction
          meta
        }
        meta
        success
        createdAt
        readedAt
        sendedAt
        sentAt
        deliveredAt
        deletedAt
        failedAt
        failedReason
        updatedAt
      }

    }
